 All enrolled subjects will receive nivolumab 3 mg/kg plus ipilimumab 1 mg/kg intravenously on day 1 of each cycle (every 3 weeks).

 Tumor assessment will be done after 6 weeks (2 cycles) and 12 weeks (4 cycles).

