Objectives: 1.

 To evaluate the efficacy, in terms of tumor shrinkage, objective response rate, and down-stage rate, of nivolumab + ipilimumab as neoadjuvant therapy for patients with HCC; 2.

 To evaluate the safety profile in patients with HCC who receive neoadjuvant nivolumab + ipilimumab treatment; 3.

 To collect HCC tumor tissue and peripheral blood samples from the patients for a comprehensive biomarker evaluation for nivolumab + ipilimumab immunotherapy.

